social_posts.post_text: Hope everyone is enjoying a light week to close off the year.  Excited to get back into an online presence again in 2023.  See you in January ❤️

GOT RUNNERS?

Sloooooooowly working my way through this stack and posting them up in stories.  We’ve got spendy antique runners, mid ranged Turkish runners and a few budget friendly distressed runners.  Take a look if you’ve been waiting for your perfect runner.
